1️⃣ Create a top-level CMakeLists.txt

This must:

set minimum version

set project name

add include/ to include paths

add the src/ folder using add_subdirectory(src)

2️⃣ Create a src/CMakeLists.txt

Inside src/CMakeLists.txt, you must:

collect .cpp files

create executable app

use the include directory defined from top-level